## Azure Availability and Resiliency ##

pricing calculator - https://azure.microsoft.com/en-in/pricing/calculator/
Chosing VM family  - https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/virtual-machines/sizes/overview?tabs=breakdownseries%2Cgeneralsizelist%2Ccomputesizelist%2Cmemorysizelist%2Cstoragesizelist%2Cgpusizelist%2Cfpgasizelist%2Chpcsizelist

Resilient - ability to still continue to work under any failure.

-  Availability Zones
   . if any zone is compromised, then the application and data will be available on other zones.
-  Availability Sets
-  VM Scale Sets
-  Load Balancer
-  Azure Storage Redundency
-  Azure Site Recovery
